{"tid":473420,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[波台數學堂]教大家循環小數點做","createTime":"2017-11-19T08:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T08:37:25.000Z","uid":21255,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c259bc2eebf17d93201b2f2555391e3b3df868a7","tid":473420,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>循環小數，是從小數部分的某一位起，一個數字或幾個數字，依次不斷地重複出現的小數。可分為有限循環小數和無限循環小數。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n10除以3<br />\n就會得出3.333333....直至無限既小數位<br />\n為左方便表達<br />\n我地會係重覆既小數上面加上小點<br />\n10除以3就會變成<br />\n　.<br />\n3.3<br />\n<br />\n我地了解左初步既做法之後，可以試下做一D練習<br />\n<br />\n學校足球校隊前鋒射了55球，只入了1球。教練想找出他的入球轉化率，希望幫他改善狀況。試以循環小數表達其入球轉化率，並以百分比表示。"},{"pid":"071c4fe99128ee3ba00bd2c95e8f41775cd40ccc","tid":473420,"uid":29764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1346b7856600c1008a472325fc87874b66ffed3","tid":473420,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有野唔明記得舉手問"},{"pid":"54a6908f941f6a187815ac9445b63f453a79f4ca","tid":473420,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36129c2d4eba1b9f5d0ff81b04f53357e4388bbd","tid":473420,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同學有野唔明唔好坐係度放底粒膠先得咖"},{"pid":"c388af2b124abfc59663ec264d96a3c289a27fe4","tid":473420,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:28:13.000Z","msg":"阿蛇真係阿蛇<img src=\"/